          "id": "283d003d1494",
          "tags": [],
          "text": "Vite config analysis for AvenOS monorepo:\n\n**Vite Config Location:** `projects/aven-ceo/vite.config.ts`\n\n**Key findings:**\n- Uses SvelteKit (`@sveltejs/kit/vite`) + Tailwind (`@tailwindcss/vite`) plugins\n- Jazz plugin is commented out/disabled\n- Custom logger silences jazz-tools broken sourcemaps\n- `envDir: repoRoot` - environment files loaded from monorepo root\n- Aliases: `@avenos/jaensen-bot` → `projects/jaensen-bot/index.ts`\n- **No explicit HMR or WebSocket configuration** - uses Vite defaults\n- Uses `loadEnv` to inject env vars into `process.env`\n\n**Project type:** SvelteKit app managed as bun workspace\n**Runtime:** bun\n\nFor HMR issues, check if SvelteKit's default HMR port (5173) is being overridden or if firewall/network is blocking WebSocket connections.",
          "updated_at": "2026-05-12T12:54:17.915824+00:00"
        },
